        "statement": "On the bridge family of Theorem 8.1, the Brauer-cocycle shift induced by a putative dark-state projector is $\\Delta c(\\delta)\\;=\\;\\mathrm{inv}_\\infty(\\mathcal{B}_\\delta)\\;-\\;\\mathrm{inv}_p(\\mathcal{B}_\\delta),\\qquad \\delta\\in\\mathbb{Z}_{\\geq 0}, where \\mathcal{B}_\\delta is the \\delta$-shifted Brauer class on the bridge fibre* (paper26-bsd §05 Step 5)",
