        "statement": "\\Sha_C := \\ker\\!\\bigl(H^1(\\mathbb{Q}, C)\\to\\prod_v H^1(\\mathbb{Q}_v, C)\\bigr) the kernel of localisation over all places* (Wiles p.\\ 2 Remark 1; paper26-bsd §02)"
