        "statement": "With P_1,\\ldots,P_r a basis of C(\\mathbb{Q})/C(\\mathbb{Q})^\\mathrm{tors}, R_\\infty := \\det\\!\\bigl(\\langle P_i, P_j\\rangle_\\mathrm{NT}\\bigr)_{1\\leq i,j\\leq r} where \\langle\\cdot,\\cdot\\rangle_\\mathrm{NT} is the Néron-Tate height pairing* (Wiles p.\\ 2; paper26-bsd §02)"
